Class 10

How to handle calendar:
1. Click on the calendar
2. locate the month and get text
3. if the desired text is not visible --> click on next
4. as soon as the desired text is found --> grab all cells from the body
5. loop through the cells
6. once the cell value is matched with our condition --> click on the matched value and break the loop

Why do we need screenshots for our testing?
In testing it is very important to take screenshots in order to prove that out test case covered certain
functionality

In selenium in order to take a screenshot we will be using TakesScreenshot interface

Actions class

Actions class is given by selenium to handle keyboard and mouse events such as:
Move to an element
Dragging and dropping
double click
right click

